The following index definition example uses the sample\_mflix.movies
collection. If you have the [Load Sample Data Into Atlas](sample-data) already
loaded on your cluster, you can use the Visual Editor or JSON (Javascript Object Notation) Editor
in the Atlas UI to configure the index. After you select your
preferred configuration method, select the database and collection,
and refine your index to add field mappings.**Basic:**Basic ExampleThe following example index definition indexes the  `year` field
as the MongoDB Search `numberFacet` type to supports queries against
that field using MongoDB Search [faceted navigation](fts-facet-ref).**Vib:**Visual Editor* In the **Add Field Mapping** window, select
  **year** from the **Field Name**
  dropdown.

* Click the **Data Type** dropdown and select
  **NumberFacet**.

* Accept the default values for the **NumberFacet
  Properties**.

* Click **Add**.**Jsonib:**JSON EditorReplace the default index definition with the following index
definition.```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": false,
    "fields": {
      "year": {
        "type": "numberFacet"
      }
    }
  }
}
```**Multitype:**Multiple Types ExampleThe following example index definition indexes the  `year`
field as the `numberFacet` and `number` types to return the
following types of results for your queries:* Metadata results for queries using MongoDB Search [faceted navigation](fts-facet-ref).

* Search results for queries using MongoDB Search operators like
  [near](near-ref), [equals](equals-ref), and [range](range-ref).**Vib:**Visual Editor* In the **Add Field Mapping** window, select
  **year** from the **Field Name**
  dropdown.

* Click the **Data Type** dropdown and select
  **NumberFacet**.

* Accept the default values for the **NumberFacet
  Properties**.

* Click **Add**.

* Repeat step **1** and select **Number** from the
  **Data Type** dropdown.

* Accept the default values for the **Number
  Properties**.

* Click **Add**.**Jsonib:**JSON EditorReplace the default index definition with the following index
definition.```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": false,
    "fields": {
      "year": [
        {
          "type": "numberFacet"
        },
        {
          "type": "number"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```
